text: Eliseo Insfrán Orué (born 27 October 1935 in Asunción, Paraguay) is a Paraguayan footballer who played for clubs in Paraguay, Colombia and Chile and for the Paraguay national football team in the FIFA World Cup in Sweden in 1958. ==Teams== * Guaraní 1954-1966 * Deportes Quindío 1966 * Libertad 1967 * O'Higgins 1968 * Sportivo Luqueño 1969-1970 ==External links== * Profile at FIFA Profile at Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Asunción Category:Paraguayan footballers Category:Paraguayan expatriate footballers Category:Paraguay international footballers Category:Paraguayan Primera División players Category:Club Guaraní players Category:Club Libertad footballers Category:Sportivo Luqueño players Category:Deportes Quindío footballers Category:O'Higgins F.C. footballers Category:Chilean Primera División players Category:1958 FIFA World Cup players Category:Expatriate footballers in Chile Category:Paraguayan expatriate sportspeople in Chile Category:Expatriate footballers in Colombia Category:Paraguayan expatriate sportspeople in Colombia Category:Association football forwards
